        "timestamp": "2018-03-23 17:53:02.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nI think in general for the logging configuration files, there is the assumption that \"ONAP\" is the component piece.  I believe it should follow this naming:\n\nPOLICY_LOGS=/var/log/onap\ncomponent-name=policy\nsubcomponent-name=pdpx | pap | console | brmsgw | ...\n\nI think as is logs would go under for example /var/log/ONAP/ONAP-PDP-REST that does not seem right to me.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
